  "selected_design_rationale": "The paper consistently centers on one proposed antenna: a rectangular microstrip patch operating at 28 GHz. The abstract, Figure 1, Table 1, results, and conclusion all align on the same geometry and performance. The beam-shaping / beam-steering discussion is an application-level array extension, not a competing final antenna geometry, so the single rectangular inset-fed patch is the canonical dominant design.",
